text: Johan Heins (born 31 July 1947) is a Dutch equestrian. He competed in the team jumping event at the 1976 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1947 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of the Netherlands Category:Equestrians at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Drenthe
